spanGrp.span: My mother was from Gerek and my father was from Bashkov.
Some people were showing girls to my father, when he wanted to marry.
babam birınji istierdi oki ävlänmäya görsädierdılär ğızlar
father -POSS.1.SG first want -IPFV -PST -PL that marry -INF -0 -DAT show COND -PST -IPFV -PST -PL girl -PL
Then they had shown him my mother.
He liked my mother, married her
After marriage he brought my mother to the city
ävländıhtan sora ee anami gätırdi shäärä
marry -CONV -ABL afterwords HESIT mother -POSS.1.SG -ACC bring -PST city -DAT
They started to live in Tbilisi.
shäärın ichında tiflisdä bashladılar kiradaidılar yapii bashladılar yashamaya
come -CONV cold -and see -PST -PL difficulties -PL -and illness -and be -PST -PL
Then after one year, I was born.
soram bir elın ichındä oldum bän
I was the first child and they loved me very much.
birınji ushağıdım choğ bäni sävierdılär bülmierdılär nä edälär hä
first child -PST.COP -1.SG much 1.SG -ACC love -IPFV -PST -PL know -IPFV -PST -PL what do -POT HESIT
My mother was looking after me and then my sister was born.
anam ävdä bahierdi bäni ushağıdım soram oldi bänim ikınji bajım soram ikınjı bajım
mother -POSS.1.SG home -LOC look -IPFV -PST 1.SG -ACC child -PST.COP -1.SG afterwords be -PST 1.SG -GEN second sister -POSS.1.SG then second sister -POSS.1.SG
My father was working while my mother was looking after us.
